data.description: SPECTACULAR House with beautiful gardens with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with pool and jacuzzi, 1-car garage and 4-car garage in front in East Palm Aire. Your home features IMPACT WINDOWS AND DOORS, newer air conditioning, newer roof, vaulted ceilings, and tile throughout. Off the living room is a large screened patio that leads to the side yard which is a great entertaining space. Off the dining room there are sliding doors leading to the pool area. This community is a hidden gem close to Turnpike, 95, casino, grocery stores and restaurants!
